GETRELIGION

NAME
        GetReligion()


SYNOPSIS
        varargs string GetReligion(int flag)


DESCRIPTION
        Returns the thing's religion. With an argument of 0 or no argument, the religion's adjective, or descriptive attribute, is returned. With an argument of 1, the religion's specific name is returned.

EXAMPLES
         


LOCATION
        /lib/chapel
/lib/classes


SEE ALSO
        SetReligion

Author
        Cratylus


